<br>
My experience with EQ has pretty much been that there are two main factions in Norrath: PC and NPC.<br>
<br>
Players seem to identify with other Players despite the fact that their avatars are of different graphic skins, etc. and do not identify with NPCs despite the similarities.  There is some sense to it, in that only the PCs can play with you.  People come up with all manner of contrivances to put disaparate characters together because the Players want to do it.<br>
<br>
It wouldn't be so bad except that frankly, too many people lack the ability to come up with something that isn't lame :-p<br>
