I have NEVER once seen an army of Dark Elf NPC soldiers pouring out of Nektulos forest and laying waste to Freeport.<br>
<br>
I have NEVER seen a group of Ogre and Troll NPCs traipsing through Rathe Mountains on their way to the Qeynos guard towers in Karana to slay humans.<br>
