The majority of the roleplay I see on FV these days is all either &quot;by the book&quot; or &quot;soap opera style love affairs&quot;.  Dark Elves who run all over and be rude to any good races.. there's REAL RP for you.. politically concious people!  Innoruuk tells me to tell you FUCK OFF!!!  Real imaginative.  I'm impressed.<br>
