<br>
To us, you're a lewt whore.  Group with who you want.  Or better yet, find yourself a different game, one where the racial tenets aren't set in place by the game's designers.  Go play Ultima online.  If you can't handle that some people may not want you in a group because they want to immerse theirselves in the world VI designed, then don't group with those people!  Find other people, and quit being so sensitive!<br>
